This document consolidates all secondary research conducted by the CDL MBA Consulting Team in support of the Clear Current Technologies GTM engagement. Research was collected across three distinct sessions using Perplexity Deep Research, TAMU library databases (IBISWorld, ABI/Inform, Orbis), EIA government data, and direct web sourcing. A fourth session independently verified the credibility of key statistics. This report is organized into ten thematic sections and includes a source credibility audit, a safe-to-use statistics reference, and a deliverable mapping guide.

