## **Databases ****&**** Sources Used**

- IBISWorld via TAMU Library — Industry surveys, market sizing, company benchmarking

- ABI/Inform Trade & Industry via TAMU — Trade journal articles on facilities staffing and maintenance

- Orbis (Moody's Analytics) via TAMU — Company financial profiles for EnergyCAP and Trane Technologies

- EIA CBECS 2018 — Commercial Buildings Energy Consumption Survey; the gold standard for commercial building energy data

- EIA Monthly Energy Review (March 2026) — Current energy pricing and consumption statistics

- EPA ENERGY STAR — Portfolio Manager adoption data, K-12 energy spending benchmarks

- FERC / State PUCs — Documented billing error enforcement actions

- Verdantix Green Quadrant 2023 — Independent competitive assessment of 15 EMS vendors

- EnergyCAP State of Utilities 2026 — Annual survey of energy and sustainability professionals

- G2 / Capterra — 132 verified user reviews of EnergyCAP used for competitive weakness documentation

- Crunchbase / Press releases — Competitor funding and valuation data (Arcadia, Verse, iem)

