## **Key Market Growth Drivers**

- Rising energy costs — 6%+ YoY increases in 2025; projected 25% electricity price increase by 2030

- ESG and sustainability mandates — California SB 253/261, EU CSRD (affecting U.S. multinationals), ISSB standards forcing investment-grade energy disclosures

- AMI proliferation — 136.9 million smart meters (~82% of U.S. electric meters as of 2024) generating interval data that legacy spreadsheet workflows cannot process

- AI integration — Verdantix 2023 Green Quadrant found all 15 leading vendors actively incorporating AI; buyers requesting predictive analytics and automated anomaly detection

- Inflation Reduction Act — $369 billion earmarked for climate initiatives, creating incentives for commercial energy management investment

